Description copied from class: AddPortCommand
This method handles the execution of adding an Attribute or a Method to a class (ClassifierRole). Therefor it uses a NavExpModelFactory to create an Attribute or Method and sets the the corresponding references to the ClassifierRole. Finally the ClassifierRoleFigure is updated.
